Robot Pilot
The Robot Pilot is a specialist trained to operate giant combat robots, power
armour, and heavy military vehicles. They combine technical knowledge with
the tactical skill to use these machines effectively in battle.

Robot Pilots begin with Robot Combat Elite as a core skill and choose two
additional vehicle specialisations. They draw from Pilot, Pilot Related,
Military, Technical, and W.P. categories.

Attribute requirements: IQ 12, PP 9.
Starting equipment: Assigned combat robot or power armour (model by background),
personal sidearm, combat jumpsuit, and radio.
